                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="237129" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 17 Nov 2018 01:26:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (green@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/32956/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/32956/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2836&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite sanity-quota, subtest test_3&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2836&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2836&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: Re-enable sanity-quota/3,6 for ZFS&lt;br/&gt;
